item_name.value: Scotch-Mount Indoor Double-Sided Mounting White Tape, 1 in x 125 in (10.4 ft), Features 3M Industrial Strength Adhesive, No Mess or Tools (314H-MED)

bullet_point.value: IDEAL FOR PAINTED DRYWALL: One of the most commonly used surfaces
STRONG BOND: Delivers a strong, permanent bond on contact
HOLDS UP TO 15 LB: Features 3M industrial strength adhesive. To hold 1 lb use 3 inches, To hold 15 lb use 45 inches
SURFACES: Designed for Painted Drywall, Finished Wood, Metal, Acrylic, Tile and Glass
EASY TO APPLY DESIGN: Great for do-it-yourself projects
NO MESS OR TOOLS: Use instead of nails and screws
APPLICATION TIPS: Ensure your surface is smooth, clean and dry for the best bond

Product Profile.tone_guidance: Use a clear, informative, and professional tone. Focus on practical details and straightforward language to assist customers in understanding the product's features and suitability for their needs.
key_attributes: Maximum holding capacity: up to 6.8 kg (using 114.3 cm of tape)
Recommended surfaces: Painted drywall, finished wood, metal, acrylic, tile, glass
No tools or mess required for application
Product Profile.product_summary: The Scotch-Mount Indoor Double-Sided Mounting Tape is a white, plastic tape roll measuring 2.54 cm wide by 317.5 cm long. It features 3M industrial strength adhesive on both sides, providing a strong, permanent bond for mounting items indoors without the need for nails or screws. Designed for use on painted drywall, finished wood, metal, acrylic, tile, and glass, it can hold up to 6.8 kg (when using 114.3 cm of tape). The tape is easy to apply, leaves no mess, and is suitable for do-it-yourself projects.

bullets.text: Keeps your workspace and home clean by leaving no mess behind after use, so mounting projects are simple and tidy. Designed for easy removal, this double-sided tape helps eliminate sticky residue and clutter, making it ideal for environments where cleanliness matters.

Offers sturdy support with a 4 mm thickness that holds items securely while staying discreet behind frames, signs, or decorations. The low-profile design ensures your mounted objects sit flush against surfaces without bulging, maintaining a neat and professional appearance.

description.text:
Experience a versatile solution for a wide range of mounting needs with this duty double sided tape from Scotch. Crafted with a 4 mm thick foam layer and strong 3M industrial adhesive on both sides, this mounting tape can be used to discreetly secure frames, signs, decorations, and more, all while maintaining a clean, uncluttered look. The easy to use permanent adhesive allows for simple application, helping you avoid the mess and hassle of traditional fasteners like nails or screws.

This foam tape is suitable for both indoor projects at home or in the office, adhering reliably to painted drywall, finished wood, metal, acrylic, tile, and glass. Whether you need a removable mounting tape option for temporary displays or a more lasting hold for heavier items, this product supports up to 6.8 kg when used as directed. The tape can be use for creative DIY tasks, organizing workspaces, or even as carpet tape to keep rugs securely in place.

Designed for convenience, the roll is lightweight and easy to handle, requiring no tools or extra materials for installation. While not water resistant and intended for indoor environments, it offers a practical alternative to nano tape and other mounting solutions. Enjoy the flexibility to reposition lightweight items or achieve a secure bond for permanent fixtures, making this mounting tape an essential addition to your supply of office and school adhesives.
